je Swaminarayan naam leshe 
tena badha paatak baadi deshe
che naam mara shruti ma anek
servopari aaj ganay ek

shadakshari mantra maha samarth 
jethi thase siddh samast aartha
sukhi kare sankat sarva kaape
ante wadi akshardham aape
jene janano vyavhaar khoto
satsang maa j ganyo maal moto
te gnyati kaje kanthi nahi tode
badam kaaje mani kaun chode

Swami Shreeji nu a gnayan
sinh garjana saman
shura hoy te sunjo 
kaan
